These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, trance, d&b
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | dubstep | metal | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, goldfish, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | fish | goldfish | pony | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, card-games, magic-tricks, reading
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | singing | card-games | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, airplane, motorbike, taxi
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | motorbike | car | airplane | taxi |

